				},
				"description": "**Acknowledge Event API**\n\nThis is a **POST API** used by a moderator to acknowledge an event.\n\n**Query Parameters**\n\n- `event_id` _(integer)_ – The unique identifier of the event to be acknowledged.\n    \n- `moderator_id` _(integer)_ – The ID of the moderator acknowledging the event.\n    \n\n**Functionality**\n\nOnce the event is acknowledged:\n\n- The **acknowledge status** is updated to **1**, indicating that the event has been acknowledged.\n    \n- The **acknowledgement timestamp** is recorded and updated in the system.\n    \n\n**Response**\n\nUpon successful acknowledgement, the API returns the following message:\n\n`Event acknowledged`"
